# 36. Complete Jenkins Pipeline

```groovy
pipeline {

 agent any

 stages {

  stage('Checkout'){
   steps{
    git 'repo'
   }
  }

  stage('Build'){
   steps{
    sh 'docker build -t app .'
   }
  }

  stage('Test'){
   steps{
    sh 'pytest'
   }
  }

  stage('Security'){
   steps{
    sh 'trivy image app'
   }
  }

  stage('Deploy'){
   steps{
    sh './deploy.sh'
   }
  }

 }
}
```

