and JavaScript automation. The pipeline automatically checked out source code, built Docker images, executed unit tests,
performed security scanning, generated artifacts, and deployed applications to Linux environments. By containerizing build 
environments and automating deployment workflows, deployment failures were reduced by 50% and release cycle time improved from 3 hours to 45 minutes.

